args.description:
Optional Firecrawl scrape parameters. If not provided, sane defaults will be used.
Examples:
- Basic: {"formats": ["markdown"]}
- With extraction: {"formats": ["json"], "json_options": {"prompt": schema_dict, more-opts-to-specify-schema}}
- See Firecrawl docs for more...: https://docs.firecrawl.dev/api-reference/endpoint/scrape
- NOTE: You would have to check the python-SDK do`cs, which changes some API field names like casing etc.
